<h1>Zurb-foundation-test</h1>
<p>This repo was created as a test to show bugs/issues with the <%= link_to 'zurb foundation', 'http://foundation.zurb.com/' %> <%= link_to 'gem', 'http://www.google.com/url?sa=t&rct=j&q=zurb%20foundation%20github&source=web&cd=1&ved=0CB0QFjAA&url=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fzurb%2Ffoundation&ei=1vxYUImFFY208ATr2IC4CA&usg=AFQjCNH5RY4eb0wZassZUNtdVaY7U9YFlg' %>.</p>

<h2>App procedure</h2>
<ol>
	<li>new rails app was created</li>
	<li>gems were added to assets ground in gemfile, as stated in the docs under <%= link_to 'Gem Versions / Rails', 'http://foundation.zurb.com/docs/gem-install.php#simple2'%></li>
	<li>edited gemfile to reflect zurb foundation 3.1</li>
	<li>ran <code>rails g foundation:install</code> and <code>rails g foundation:layout</code> as per docs under <%= link_to 'Gem Versions / Rails', 'http://foundation.zurb.com/docs/gem-install.php#simple2'%></li>
	<li>created controller with actions for this page and templates, copied from <%= link_to 'templates', 'http://foundation.zurb.com/templates.php' %>.</li>
</ol>

